extends layout

block content
  h3 Genre Search
  h5 route: "/api/genre"
  h5 return: JSON
  h5 format: /api/genre?list={list_of_genres}
  br
  h4 
    u Filter Parameters

  h5 By list
  a(href="/api?list=action|romance")
    /api?title=Zero_no_Tsukaima 
  p 
    | This parameter 
    b must be present 
    | to continue. The values are separated by a 
    b pipe ("|")
    | character. It is 
    b case-insensitive.

  br

  h4 
    u JSON properties

  h5 genres
  p (STRING) The list of genres that have been queried.

  h5 titles
  p (LIST) JSON data of the titles.
  ul
    li 
      h5 title
      p (STRING) title name of the book
    li 
      h5 page
      p (STRING) interwiki main page title of the book.
    li 
      h5 lastreviseddate
      p (STRING) The data and time of the last revision, in UTC+0.
    li 
      h5 lastrevisedid
      p (NUMBER) the unique id of the last revison.
    li 
      h5 pageid
      p (NUMBER) the unique id of the main page of the book

  br
  h4 Example JSON 
  a(href="/api/genre?list=shoujo|comedy")
    code /api/genre?list=shoujo|comedy
  br
